ref:_00D7091pB._500Q000BwzBL:ref

Hello,
According to the documentation: https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Solutions/Databases/SQL/Collection/2-SQL_SensitiveDataScan.htm
The only dependency for SQL seems to be having the Sensitive data scan on the audit server. The Add-on on the target looks like a requirement for a filesystem scan, which we don't need at this time.

We are thinking this could be related to the recent upgrade to the newest version.
Could we get Kurt Gerth to help us with this ticket? as he guided us through that process.

Regards
